124
00:12:13.670 --> 00:12:15.240
How many?

125
00:12:15.240 --> 00:12:16.870
Need you ask?

126
00:12:16.870 --> 00:12:20.000
Astrologer, you must at least know how to count.

127
00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:21.720
