135
00:12:42.210 --> 00:12:44.870
This is extremely rare!

136
00:12:44.870 --> 00:12:46.480
A Tri-solar Syzygy.

137
00:12:46.480 --> 00:12:49.550
Thus, our planet and the three suns

138
00:12:49.550 --> 00:12:58.170
