143
00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:20.790
My greatest, most honorable Emperor, this is the most propitious sign!

144
00:13:20.790 --> 00:13:24.510
Now that the three suns are orbiting around our planet,

145
00:13:24.510 --> 00:13:27.030
