147
00:13:29.750 --> 00:13:33.440
Let me double-check the calculations.

148
00:13:33.440 --> 00:13:36.610
I'll... I'll prove this!

149
00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:43.690
Von Neumann, what do you think about this phenomenon?

150
00:13:43.690 --> 00:13:49.240
Your Majesty, it wasn't included in any of the previous calculations.

151
00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:52.880
-. I'll try to... 
 - Report!

